# 11. `kubernetes/` — K8s Deployment

## Purpose

Deploy application on Kubernetes.

---

## Example File

```plaintext id="jlwm2l"
kubernetes/deployment.yaml
```

---

## Example YAML

```yaml id="jkwcz5"
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment

metadata:
  name: high-performance-app

spec:
  replicas: 2

  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: high-performance-app

  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: high-performance-app

    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: high-performance-app
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
```

---

# Deploy Command

```bash id="8vuvg0"
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
```

